  "title": "Enterprise Architect/ Solution Architect (Cloud, Digital)",
  "description": "<p> </p><p><strong>Enterprise Architect/ Solution Architect (Cloud, Digital)</strong><br /></p><p>As a <strong>Enterprise Architect/ Solution Architect (Cloud, Digital),</strong> you will lead the Solution for government transformation projects. You will ensure integration of enterprise platforms, drive innovation with AI-enabled solutions, and support the digital government vision of Singapore.</p><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Strong involvement as Enterprise Architect/ Solution Architect.</strong></li><li><strong>Technically incline in Software Application Design and Implementation.</strong></li><li><strong>Good in Software/ Solution Architectural Design and Implementation.</strong></li><li>Knowledge of Software Application Solution is Preferred.</li><li><strong>Strong knowledge of Cloud Platform (AWS, Azure, GCP).</strong></li><li><li>Lead the solution architecture design for enterprise-grade digital applications, including workflow systems, case management, portals, and data platforms.</li></li><li>Experience in handling Digital Solution and Digital Transformation.</li><li>Good in handling Solution Architectural Design and Implementation.</li><li>Good in Stakeholders/ Clients Management.</li><li>Experience with AI-enabled solutions, cloud-based platforms and digital transformation.</li><li><strong>Min. 10+ years of proven leadership in solution architecture, enterprise software delivery, public-sector projects, or digital transformation.</strong></li><li>Strong experience designing and delivering enterprise application platforms, with an emphasis on complex systems integration and multi-agency solutions.</li><li>Experience in high level design, implementation and technical requirements management.</li><li>Possess Government / System Integrator domain (Preferred).</li><li>Singaporeans only!</li></ul><p><br /><br /></p><p>If you feel that you have the skill-sets that we are looking for, please apply in-confidence with an updated MS Word Resume to: jeline@starcareerconsulting.com</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidate would be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Yong Jeline (Reg. No. R1101621)</strong></p><p><strong>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</strong></p>",
